{"generated": "2026-07-19 12:36", "brief": "<b>1. 레버리지 ETF 상장폐지 관련 정책 불확실성</b>\n김용범 정책실장은 단일종목 레버리지 ETF의 상장폐지가 현실적으로 어렵다는 입장을 여러 차례 밝히며, 시장 충격을 최소화하기 위한 추가 보완책 마련을 시사했다. 이는 관련 상품 투자자들에게 중요한 정책 방향을 제시하는 동시에, 시장 전반에 미칠 영향을 고려한 신중한 접근을 보여준다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiYkFVX3lxTE5PODZWWE9IY2F3QjNObENpci04UHNidFBBRFBJYmtBQk91NTJwOHVQNW12dW9LY1ZMdGdKN2pvTFAtNnJUT0pVdDJRM3VZOVVDeGJaeTlhNnRDU1oybHljUUR3?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#5</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMidEFVX3lxTE4yMHFSYnYxSG9QQmpFNll1RG9fN1RHN0g5Qm5wZExmcGlCVS1DSWhNV0Ywc0o3bFRyZnYzd3JQY0RfbEtNbkJwckJHcC1rcnJvSnN1SW9QeFpSdUlLZGxnRS1HUWx0SUdTcEJiNWRMb21ZQWtu?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#8</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXEFVX3lxTE8wcFEwR1VZdVd2QVdodHUwNV8zQmx0QWxfNjdZb2NBOGtnSXQxV0UtdnZaTEp2azVmdmpTUVJPeHptUlg4b2tlanlXZmVXeGlOcTRrUXpITTJEd1F1?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#9</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#10</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiaEFVX3lxTFBLQ1NyNHZrN01qM25sSzFQSWpEdTc3c2x4UU9zN3dXRGtVbXV3VHRNRzlITHR0b2h3aHlZTWJaZ2k5U1phLUJyZXp5VWNLTVVac3RxWl80WjltcWVnV0JNam9FUzVQUGpt?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#11</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXEFVX3lxTE1iQlV0VUpIVS1kakw4UTdpRUh1S3VrRzRZek9qYjl6a04wRVhmWFJVcVcwM2tENGNIN08tcHRUTEpaUEI5MjU0RGNDX2lmUklvRDg1MFptbWxER0RF?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#12</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMib0FVX3lxTE9FeS1ZbUxFOFpJbkVHSzdLUGRzbXFvZU9nUUwyZXhkOUxibko0cE9ENnFOdjlKNGlHY01aQU5fZzlDMEo0alNrZllkekV5SVVxZENKX0RVMGF3cGd1Z2lGS3F5VU1yamVJektaR3dQYw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#13</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiUkFVX3lxTE5nYzQyd2pGeUhqOThCRGRhYnAxZUV6cE1ZNldMbVNZcFlKeno4bUYtNWVQdHhKTFFFeHA3cFJ1VDFBYUNfakEwWjNfaGszN3ppMHc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#14</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.c